ArchBang: Donations
===================

ArchBang is built and maintained by one developer. Every donation directly supports
ongoing development, server costs, and hardware testing.


What Your Support Covers
------------------------

  - Server hosting and bandwidth for ISO distribution
  - Testing across different hardware configurations
  - Time for new features, bug fixes, and keeping current with Arch updates


